Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要著急 仔細看說明書
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,適應了就用專用的筆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在線縫的部位滲線即可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.59,0:00:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如此看起來更立體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真實感就出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,今天到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大家回去時注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,賽麗亞姐姐再見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我是北條理央
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,賽麗亞請做我的鋼普拉師父
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:00:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,來 請看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是鋼彈社羣的主街道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 別拽我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 就像去遊樂園的小孩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,賽麗亞才是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,居然選這樣的造型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是把以前的試做拿出來的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 不是要給我帶路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,賽麗亞明明有賬號為甚麼不登入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不擅長數碼產品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.49,0:01:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,關於對戰 也不適應
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來我想去鋼彈基地買模型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然入門級也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但我還是想直接挑戰寫真級
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只要理央開心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,鋼普拉就是自由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,自由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能樂在其中便好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,鋼彈元宇宙正是為此建立的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這裡是夢想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,面具女士居然是賽麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那個對手是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,從頭開始講吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道川口女士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,女鋼普拉師的最高榮譽是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾經為了那個稱號而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,和妹妹瑪麗亞一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,勝者 賽麗亞潤月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,成功晉級決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我在決賽等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那個裝備是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,擅自用姐姐的裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,還輸了比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我放棄決賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這算甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要總是可憐我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不把我當回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒那意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那天后我就放棄了鋼普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,下定決心放下一切再也不牽扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,遠房親戚的傑夫叔擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,推薦我在這工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因為只是製作模型就接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但我還是沒去元宇宙參加對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但為甚麼願意陪我去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是作為賽麗亞還是面具女士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,以純粹的熱情去漫遊鋼普拉世界的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我在那個世界太有名了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以得隱藏一下身份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但也到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞還在恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我還不能繼續玩鋼普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這也太怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不是討厭鋼普拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,沒資格被稱為師父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我的師父都是賽麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不希望她放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,突然尖叫禮貌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,路過的熱心姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,放不下獨自煩惱的可愛男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有那麼明顯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,或者說是有那種氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,無邪的青春芳香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,吸引了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,來光顧一下我的店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好了走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好好傾訴你青春期的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是賽麗亞的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你認識師父嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,之前有過交際
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫理央
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我是馬吉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她現在怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她還在避諱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和瑪麗亞溝通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,賽麗亞是了不起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是我重要的師父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,為了能向瑪麗亞傳達我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要再提高水準
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,對方可是有實力角逐川口女士的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要去做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,討伐領主的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面戰鬥很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,能積累很多經驗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不太簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但稍微有點冒險才刺激對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的眼神不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,領主在中央的天空神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,討伐先到先得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但首先要打掃戰場的敵人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,數量很多 要做好準備哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,理央北條
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,燦陽鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,能打到甚麼地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,又拉了個新人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真樂此不疲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 文奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,說得好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只是幫幫為師父努力的小夥而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:10:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,數量太多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,別說撐到領主了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,上面還有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣對付獨眼就沒完沒了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,核心鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是創形者的悠人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,和我想的一樣 不錯的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,戰場1 任務完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色的核心鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,挺不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你好悠人 我叫理央
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,變形機關和機動性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這出色的模型是經驗和技術的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,隨我同去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,此次任務目標是討伐領主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得組隊效率比較高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,倒也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但為甚麼和我組隊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我還經驗尚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,從你的模型就能看出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這是精心打磨的好機體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是師父教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,鋼彈從頭再來的機會多的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是享受過程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是個好師父啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,模型也在看著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,模型也一定會回應你的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,模型也在看著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,出發吧 理央
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不容錯過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可愛弟子正挑戰超難的討伐領主任務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 賽麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是收其為徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就要盡師父的職責守望到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,傑夫叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是天空神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧理央
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是領主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,攻擊就像刮痧一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那就近戰解決它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫 冥王星裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,核心轉換
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,著裝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,冥王星九型鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,漆黑的鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,用回收塑膠做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想試試實戰能發揮多少效能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,面對如此巨大的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,卻毫無懼色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,相信模型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,模型便會回應你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧 燦陽鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,薙刀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊就交給我吧 悠人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,悠人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有撒手鐧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,任務完成 恭喜通關
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,悠人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,悠人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你理央
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了你取勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不至於 我能力還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,確實還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不夠但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,鋼普拉會回應你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊的領主戰也燃起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好了上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和強者過招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,來和我神木世海比劃比劃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,尊者鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,神木世海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那個日本冠軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是本人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,世海君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,突然冒出來搞甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,想比比打贏領主的玩家誰更強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,賽麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,誰要和我過招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是冠軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,擊敗領主的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我想和你對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我是為了變強而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,非常強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,正面角力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是模型對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看著打得挺暢快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,竟有這般實力 真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可以毫無保留地使出奧義了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,燦陽鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,神木模型流奧義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,炎王斬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,盡興了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你理央
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我才該謝你世海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興能和你全力過招
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 下次再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好 期待下次對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,收穫不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,精神又提起來不少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了 世海太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,文奈？ 不沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:21:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:21:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,您來看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.56,0:22:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,現在差不多可以拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,近期會有大規模的對戰活動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞肯定也會參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我會下戰書
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,能幫我應對瑪麗亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.33,0:22:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Comment
